('55804','19578','5','Romantic finca hotel near Santa Maria with marvellous views of the Tramuntana mountains'),
('55805','19579','5','The manor house dating back to 1500 and 1995 was the last time completely restored and rebuilt, with the authentic materials were obtained. In recent years, minor repairs were carried out regularly and replaced the roof.\r\nThe property has an area of about 960 m² and stands on a 21,100 m² plot with fruit trees and pine forest. The currently used as a private residence property but you can use it as a country house hotel, as it has 10 double rooms and one suite. On the ground floor entrance are with reception, dining room, fireplace room, hotel quality kitchen, utility room, 3 double bedrooms with a bathroom suite, covered outdoor patios and cloakrooms. On the 1st floor there are a further 5 double bedrooms (suite) with en suite bathroom. The spacious terraces leads to the Mediterranean garden with pool area (pool 12x5,5m). The property is supplied with its own well water. The planted on the property 650 olive, orange and almond trees can hereby be irrigated. Hotel guests can park their vehicles in one of the hotel''s parking. The solar-assisted oil central heating makes for cozy warmth.\r\nThe main building and a neighboring building with 2 suites and double rooms need a complete refurbishment to bring it structurally to the present standard. Total cost about € 1 million. The property is passed without furniture and decoration, but with a professional kitchen equipment.\r\nTo Palma -Inca highway is only a 2 minute drive to the airport and about 20 minutes drive.'),
